---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Contribute - Surf Deeper" description="How to contribute guides and spots using our content system: folders, sections, ordering, and Markdown formatting.">

  <header class="page-header">
    <h1>Contribute</h1>
    <p class="page-subtitle">Share your knowledge, help the community</p>
    <div style="margin: 1.5rem 0;">
      <a href="https://github.com/surfdeeper/surfdeeper" target="_blank" style="display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 1rem; justify-content: center;">
        <img src="https://github.githubassets.com/images/modules/logos_page/GitHub-Mark.png" alt="GitHub Logo" width="48" height="48" style="background: #fff; border-radius: 50%; padding: 4px;" />
        <span style="font-size: 1.25rem; font-weight: 700; color: #00ff88;">github.com/surfdeeper/surfdeeper</span>
      </a>
    </div>
  </header>


  <section class="github-contribution">
    <h2>Contributing Made Easy</h2>
    <p>Follow these simple steps to start contributing, even if you're new to coding!</p>
    <div class="contribution-steps">
      <div class="step-card">
        <h3>1. Download VS Code</h3>
        <p><a href="https://code.visualstudio.com/" target="_blank">Visual Studio Code</a> is a free code editor for Windows, Mac, and Linux.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="step-card">
        <h3>2. Sign Up for GitHub</h3>
        <p><a href="https://github.com/" target="_blank">Create a free account</a> to contribute and track your changes.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="step-card">
        <h3>3. Set Up Copilot</h3>
        <p>In VS Code, go to <b>Extensions</b> and install <a href="https://marketplace.visualstudio.com/items?itemName=GitHub.copilot" target="_blank">GitHub Copilot</a>. Sign in with your GitHub account.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="step-card">
        <h3>4. Fork & Clone the Repo</h3>
        <p>
          <a href="https://github.com/surfdeeper/surfdeeper" target="_blank">Go to the repo</a> and click <b>Fork</b>.<br>
          Then, copy your repo link and run:<br>
          <span class="code-block">git clone https://github.com/YOUR-USERNAME/surfdeeper.git</span>
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="step-card">
        <h3>5. Add/Edit Guides & Spots</h3>
        <p>Edit or add Markdown files in <code>src/content/guides/</code> or <code>src/content/spots/</code>. Copilot will help you write!</p>
      </div>
      <div class="step-card">
        <h3>6. Commit & Push</h3>
        <p>In the terminal, run:<br><span class="code-block">git add .<br>git commit -m "Add new guide/spot"<br>git push origin main</span></p>
      </div>
      <div class="step-card">
        <h3>7. Make a Pull Request</h3>
        <p>Go to your fork on GitHub, click <b>Compare & pull request</b>, add a description, and submit!</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <p style="margin-top:2rem; text-align:center;">
      <a href="https://github.com/surfdeeper/surfdeeper" target="_blank" class="contribute-link" style="font-size:1.2rem;">Visit the Project Repo</a>
    </p>
  </section>

  <section class="article">
    <h2>Update Spot Coordinates</h2>
    <p>If you notice a spot's pin is in the wrong location on the map:</p>
    <ol>
      <li>Go to the <a href="/maps">Spots page</a></li>
      <li>Click on the spot marker to open the popup</li>
      <li>Click "üìç Pin in wrong location?"</li>
      <li>Drag the pin to the correct location</li>
      <li>Click "Done - Show Instructions" to get the new coordinates</li>
      <li>Follow the GitHub link to submit your correction</li>
    </ol>
    <p>The coordinates are stored in the frontmatter of each spot's markdown file at <code>src/content/spots/</code>.</p>
  </section>

  <section class="article">
    <h2>How it works</h2>
    <p>Keep it simple. Follow existing patterns. That‚Äôs it.</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Put guides in <code>src/content/guides/&lt;section&gt;/&lt;slug&gt;.md</code></li>
      <li>Frontmatter: <code>title</code> (required), <code>description</code> and <code>order</code> (optional)</li>
      <li>Sections = folder names; display labels and order live in <a href="https://github.com/surfdeeper/surfdeeper/blob/main/src/content/guides/_sections.json" target="_blank">_sections.json</a></li>
      <li>Sorting: by <code>order</code>, then by <code>title</code></li>
    </ul>
    <p>Schema lives in <a href="https://github.com/surfdeeper/surfdeeper/blob/main/src/content/config.ts" target="_blank">content config</a>. Browse existing files in the <a href="https://github.com/surfdeeper/surfdeeper/tree/main/src/content/guides" target="_blank">guides folder</a> and copy the closest example.</p>
  </section>

  <section class="article">
    <h2>Quick steps</h2>
    <ol>
      <li>Open the <a href="https://github.com/surfdeeper/surfdeeper/tree/main/src/content/guides" target="_blank">guides folder</a>.</li>
      <li>Copy an existing file in the right section; rename with a clear slug.</li>
      <li>Edit the <code>title</code> and content; add <code>order</code> if you want to control position.</li>
      <li>Open a PR. We‚Äôll review quickly.</li>
    </ol>
  </section>

  <section class="article">
    <h2>PR workflow (short)</h2>
    <p>Use the GitHub UI for quick edits, or develop locally with <code>npm run dev</code>. Keep changes small and follow existing patterns. Link sources when helpful.</p>
  </section>

</Layout>

<style>
  .page-header {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }

  .page-header h1 {
    color: #00ff88;
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
  }

  .page-subtitle {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    color: #00ff88;
    font-weight: 500;
  }

  .contribution-types h2,
  .article h2 {
    color: #00ff88;
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    border-bottom: 2px solid #00ff88;
    padding-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .contribution-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
    gap: 1.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }

  .contribution-card {
    background-color: #1e293b;
    border: 2px solid #334155;
    border-radius: 8px;
    padding: 1.5rem;
    transition: border-color 0.3s ease;
  }

  .contribution-card:hover {
    border-color: #00ff88;
  }

  .contribution-card h3 {
    color: #00ff88;
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .contribution-card p {
    color: #00ff88;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    opacity: 0.9;
  }

  .contribution-card ul {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .contribution-card li {
    color: #00ff88;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    padding-left: 1rem;
    position: relative;
  }

  .contribution-card li::before {
    content: "‚Üí";
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    color: #00cc6a;
  }

  .contribute-link {
    display: inline-block;
    background-color: #00ff88;
    color: #0f172a;
    padding: 0.5rem 1rem;
    border-radius: 6px;
    text-decoration: none;
    font-weight: 600;
    transition: background-color 0.3s ease;
  }

  .contribute-link:hover {
    background-color: #00cc6a;
  }

  .article {
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto 2rem;
  }
  .article p, .article li {
    color: #00ff88;
    opacity: 0.95;
  }
  .article ul, .article ol {
    margin-left: 1rem;
  }

  /* remove extra cardy blocks */

  .github-contribution {
    background-color: #1e293b;
    border: 2px solid #334155;
    border-radius: 8px;
    padding: 2rem;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }

  .templates .code-block {
    display: block;
    background: #0f172a;
    color: #d1fae5;
    padding: 1rem;
    border-radius: 6px;
    border: 1px solid #334155;
    white-space: pre-wrap;
  }

  .github-contribution h2 {
    color: #00ff88;
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .github-contribution p {
    color: #00ff88;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .contribution-steps {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr));
    gap: 1.5rem;
  }

  .step-card {
    background-color: #0f172a;
    border: 2px solid #334155;
    border-radius: 8px;
    padding: 1.5rem;
    transition: border-color 0.3s ease;
  }

  .step-card:hover {
    border-color: #00ff88;
  }

  .step-card h3 {
    color: #00ff88;
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .step-card p {
    color: #00ff88;
    margin: 0;
    opacity: 0.9;
  }

  .step-card a {
    color: #00cc6a;
    text-decoration: none;
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  .step-card a:hover {
    color: #00ff88;
  }

  .contact-info {
    background-color: #1e293b;
    border: 2px solid #334155;
    border-radius: 8px;
    padding: 2rem;
  }

  .contact-info p {
    color: #00ff88;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .contact-methods {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(200px, 1fr));
    gap: 1.5rem;
  }

  .contact-method {
    text-align: center;
  }

  .contact-method h4 {
    color: #00ff88;
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .contact-method p {
    color: #00ff88;
    opacity: 0.9;
    margin: 0;
  }
</style>
